bo‘lishi shart, ammo biz birontasini 
yaratish haqida qayg‘urmasak ham bo‘ladi.

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:27.150
Demak, biz Android Studio da bironta 
yangi ilova yaratganimizda 

00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:30.160
