Shunga o‘xshab, manifest fayl ham 
bir joyda butun ilova haqidagi 

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.105
muhim ma’lumotlarni xulosalab beradi.

00:00:46.105 --> 00:00:49.065
Qachonki siz ilovangizni bironta qurilmaga o‘rnatganingizda, 
u ilovangizdagi bironta kodni ishlatishidan oldin 

00:00:49.065 --> 00:00:52.315
Android sistema birinchi 
bo‘lib bu faylga qaraydi.

00:00:52.315 --> 00:00:53.746
Shunday qilib, bu fayl nimadan tashkil topgan?

00:00:53.746 --> 00:00:57.625
Oxirgi mashqdan barcha activity lar 
Android manifest faylda

00:00:57.625 --> 00:00:59.066
ro‘yxatdan o‘tkazilishi kerakligini payqagansiz.
Xo‘sh, bu manifest fayl ham 

00:00:59.066 --> 00:01:03.642
boshqa muhim ma’lumotlar, misol uchun, ilovaning 
yagona ifodalovchisi bo‘lgan package nomi, 

00:01:03.642 --> 00:01:08.182
ilovaning komponentlari, ya’ni activity nomlari, 
istaklar, xabarnoma yoki kameradan foydalanish 

00:01:08.182 --> 00:01:12.511
uchun ruxsatlardan iborat
va u yana eng kichik hajmdagi 

00:01:12.511 --> 00:01:17.861
Android API ni o‘rnatishga yordam beradi, 
bu ilova 

00:01:17.861 --> 00:01:22.251
Android platformasining qaysi versiyasiga 
to‘g‘ri kelishini aniqlash deganidir.

00:01:22.251 --> 00:01:26.511
Shunday qilib, bizning Miwok ilovamiz uchun manifest 
faylda, mana bu yerda package nomi berilgan

00:01:26.511 --> 00:01:28.147
va ular ilovamizning komponentlaridir.

00:01:28.147 --> 00:01:30.971
Bu ilovamizning mavzusiga ishora 
qiladi, bu style.xml 

00:01:30.971 --> 00:01:34.861
fayliga murojaat qilingandagi
ilova mavzusi, shuning uchun ham ilovamiz 

00:01:34.861 --> 00:01:39.320
va holatlar paneli malla tusga kiradi, va 
bu yerda ikonkamiz aniqlanadi.

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:43.200
Bizning qurilmamizdagi ilovaning barcha oynasida, 
bizning Miwok ilovamiz uchun ilova ikonkasi 

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.380
sifatida savatchani ko‘ramiz.

00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:47.820
Miwok ilovasida, bizda mana bu yerda 
ko‘rsatilgan beshta activity mavjud.

00:01:47.820 --> 00:01:52.070
MainActivity tegida, biz yana intent filter 
deb nomlanadigan nimanidir ko‘ramiz.

00:01:52.070 --> 00:01:56.020
Eslab qoling intent boshqa bir ilova 
tomonidan namoyish qilinadigan harakatning 

00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:57.800
ba’zi bir turi uchun talab qilinadigan xabar.

00:01:57.800 --> 00:02:02.060
O‘z navbatida, ilovalar boshqa ilovalarni e’lon qilishda 
intent filter larni belgilab qo‘ya oladi, 

00:02:02.060 --> 00:02:05.730
