bironta harakatni amalga oshira olaman deyman.

00:02:05.730 --> 00:02:08.220
Asosiy harakat va kategoriyani ishga tushiruvchi 
bu intent filter 

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:12.100
bu ilovamizga kiruvchi nuqta ekanligini ko‘rsatadi.

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:15.905
Qachonki, foydalanuvchi qurilmaning home ekranidagi 
Miwok ilovasining ikonkasi ustiga bossa, 

00:02:15.905 --> 00:02:18.145
Android ilovamizni boshlash uchun 
intent jo‘natadi, ya’ni xohish bildiradi.

00:02:18.145 --> 00:02:21.465
Bu activity o‘sha intent ni 
qabul qiladi va ekranni ochadi.

00:02:21.465 --> 00:02:24.415
Bizda keyinroq bu darsda Android manifest.xml 
faylni o‘zgartirishni amalyotda 

00:02:24.415 --> 00:02:27.395
